{"tid":1418541,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要求你班冷氣軍師立即同前線義士道歉 ！","createTime":"2019-08-05T19:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T20:01:43.000Z","uid":30555,"like":80,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"505b22be920c1733a9f089508d5e206abeb5df47","tid":1418541,"uid":30555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:06:44.000Z","msg":"隔離post係到抹黑前線竟然可以過萬正評 食撚懵左你班連登仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我認同大家係開始因為仇警而有d失焦 但係見到無啦啦老屈義士話佢地戀棧權力我真係睇到眼火爆！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請問依家前線義士得到乜撚野權力咁巴閉？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇啊仆街！</span></span></strong><br />\n個個上得前線 都知道自己做緊d咩 會有d咩後果要承擔 受傷既受傷 被捕既被捕 好彩冇事既都奔波左成日 返到屋企攰到死 打開個連登 仲要比班冷氣軍師話享受權力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得突然之間轉風向屌前線呢件事好鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家真係諗下咪比人亂帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"8dc6ebee89bbc32f5156f1987abfd16e315e73f7","tid":1418541,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:07:36.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"480f9613782e8f55c185aa567cf6af48232e15b2","tid":1418541,"uid":6061,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:08:06.000Z","msg":"放核彈都唔割!"},{"pid":"5b44492ed4ffe925f0a8d05fbdd8acc6e44f3fcd","tid":1418541,"uid":5258,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:09:42.000Z","msg":"我冷氣軍師+和理非<br />\n但前線放核彈揸高達都唔割<br />\n今晚好多5毛風向撚<br />\n前線勇武唔好畀佢地打擊到<br />\n我地支持你地"},{"pid":"19d84dc804791a8174a3a5fe55b759442e01b4b1","tid":1418541,"uid":30555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re